```

## **Accessibility**

```typescript
// ✅ DO: Add aria-labels for screen readers when needed
<Button aria-label="클래스 시작">
  <Play className="w-4 h-4 mr-2" />
  클래스 시작
</Button>

// ✅ DO: Use semantic icons that match their purpose
<Mic className="w-4 h-4" /> // For voice/audio features
<Target className="w-4 h-4" /> // For goals/targeting
```

## **Korean UI Context**

- Icons should complement Korean text without overwhelming it
- Use consistent sizing to maintain visual hierarchy
- Ensure icons are culturally appropriate for Korean users
- Maintain sufficient spacing between icons and Korean text